     <script>

  var players = [];

  var tag = document.createElement('script');

  tag.src = "https://www.youtube.com/iframe_api";

  var firstScriptTag = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];

  firstScriptTag.parentNode.insertBefore(tag, firstScriptTag);



  function onPlayerReady(){

  }


  function videoPausedMode(video){
      var playerContainer = $(video).closest(".video-with-cover-container");

      $(playerContainer).addClass("video-paused").removeClass("video-playing");

  }


  function videoPlayingMode(video){
      var playerContainer = $(video).closest(".video-with-cover-container");

      $(playerContainer).addClass("video-playing video-started").removeClass("video-paused");
  }




  function onPlayerStateChange(event){

      switch(event.data)
      {
            case YT.PlayerState.PLAYING:
                videoPlayingMode(event.target.a);
            break;

            case YT.PlayerState.PAUSED:
                videoPausedMode(event.target.a);
            break;

            case YT.PlayerState.ENDED:
            break;

      }

  }


  function onYouTubeIframeAPIReady(){

    $("iframe").each(function(){

      var playerId = $(this).attr("id");

      console.log("player ID: ", playerId);

      players.push(new YT.Player(playerId, {
        events: {
          'onReady': onPlayerReady,
          'onStateChange': onPlayerStateChange
        }
      }));


      console.log("Initialized Player: ", YT.get(playerId));

      console.log("Players: ", players);

    });

  }


  function pauseYouTubeVideos(){
    if(Array.isArray(players))
    {
      $.each(players, function(){
        console.log("YouTube Video loop: ", this);
        this.pauseVideo();
      });
    }
  }

</script>
